npmPackage.name: @westegg/gatsby-theme-misk
npmPackage.description: This theme extends [@westegg/gatsby-theme-digital-garden](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@westegg/gatsby-theme-digital-garden) using React components from the [Misk-Web](https://cashapp.github.io/misk-web/).

childMarkdownRemark.html:
@westegg/gatsby-theme-digital-garden

This theme extends @westegg/gatsby-theme-digital-garden using React components from the Misk-Web.

It serves as the theme for the official Misk-Web docs site.

This Gatsby Theme lives in Westegg.
